        <div class="armak-value-title">Built to Standard</div>
        <div class="armak-value-desc">ANSI/TIA-compliant installs. Every cable tested, every port labeled, every job documented to spec.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="armak-value armak-reveal" data-num="02" style="--delay: 0.18s;">
